WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.000
Creating your RestoreAssist account takes less than 2 minutes.

00:08.000 --> 00:16.000
Enter your email, create a secure password, add your business name and ABN.

00:16.000 --> 00:20.304
We verify your ABN automatically.

00:20.304 --> 00:28.304
Check your email for a verification code, enter it, and you're in.

00:28.304 --> 00:36.304
The Setup Wizard then guides you through activating your workspace.

00:36.304 --> 00:41.783
Start managing restoration projects today.